"title": "5461: prisoners",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5461",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>People who have been deprived of their liberty and confined against their will.</p>\n<h2>People imprisoned out of anger, envy or jealousy</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:24\">GEN 37:24</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer52:11\">JER 52:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen39:19\">GEN 39:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen40:3\">GEN 40:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:14\">GEN 41:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen42:16\">GEN 42:16</a>JDG <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen16:21\">16:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg16:25\">JDG 16:25</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:4\">2KI 17:4</a> <em>Hoshea, king of Israel</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs25:18\">2KI 25:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr28:5\">2CH 28:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr28:17\">2CH 28:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr33:11\">2CH 33:11</a> <em>Manasseh</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa14:17\">ISA 14:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa20:4\">ISA 20:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:9\">HAB 1:9</a></p>\n<h2>People imprisoned for lawlessness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra7:26\">EZR 7:26</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:16\">MAT 27:16</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:6-Mark15:7\">MRK 15:6–15:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:19\">LUK 23:19</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:29\">EXO 12:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:22-Isa42:24\">ISA 42:22–42:24</a></p>\n<h2>People imprisoned for their faithfulness to God</h2>\n<h3>Micaiah</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:27\">1KI 22:27</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr18:26\">2CH 18:26</a></p>\n<h3>Hanani, seer to Asa</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr16:10\">2CH 16:10</a></p>\n<h3>Jeremiah</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:2\">JER 32:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer33:1\">JER 33:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer37:15\">JER 37:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer37:18\">JER 37:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer37:21\">JER 37:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer38:6\">JER 38:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer38:9\">JER 38:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer39:15\">JER 39:15</a></p>\n<h3>John the Baptist</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:12\">MAT 4:12</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:14\">MRK 1:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:2\">MAT 11:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:3\">MAT 14:3</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:17\">MRK 6:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:10\">MAT 14:10</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:27\">MRK 6:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:20\">LUK 3:20</a></p>\n<h3>The apostles</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:18\">ACT 5:18</a></p>\n<h3>Simon Peter</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:5\">ACT 12:5</a></p>\n<h3>The early Christian believers</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:3\">ACT 8:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:21\">ACT 9:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts22:4\">ACT 22:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts22:19\">ACT 22:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:10\">ACT 26:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:34\">HEB 10:34</a></p>\n<h3>Paul</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:4\">ACT 12:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts22:27\">ACT 22:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts23:29\">ACT 23:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts28:17\">ACT 28:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:5\">2CO 6:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:23\">2CO 11:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:1\">EPH 3:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:1\">EPH 4:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phlm1:1\">PHM 1:1</a></p>\n<h3>Paul and Silas</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:23-Acts16:24\">ACT 16:23–16:24</a></p>\n<h3>Aristarchus</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:10\">COL 4:10</a></p>\n<h3>Epaphras</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phlm1:23\">PHM 1:23</a></p>\n<h3>The saints of old</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:36\">HEB 11:36</a></p>\n<h2>Figurative and poetic use of imprisonment</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:22-Gal3:23\">GAL 3:22–3:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps142:7\">PSA 142:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa24:22\">ISA 24:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:6-Isa42:7\">ISA 42:6–42:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:22\">ISA 42:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek19:9\">EZK 19:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech9:11-Zech9:12\">ZEC 9:11–9:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:30\">MAT 18:30</a></p>\n<h2>The LORD does not abandon prisoners</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps79:11\">PSA 79:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen39:21\">GEN 39:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps68:6\">PSA 68:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps69:33\">PSA 69:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps102:20\">PSA 102:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:10\">PSA 107:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps146:7\">PSA 146:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:8-Isa49:9\">ISA 49:8–49:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:1\">ISA 61:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:31-Lam3:36\">LAM 3:31–3:36</a></p>\n<h2>Christians should show concern for prisoners</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:3\">HEB 13:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:36\">MAT 25:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:39\">MAT 25:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:43\">MAT 25:43</a></p>",
